snippet.title: UGH! C64 Longplay [160] Full Playthrough / Walkthrough (no commentary) #c64 #retrogaming
snippet.description:
Longplay of the 1983 C64 classic UGH!, one of many early 80s caveman themed games but certainly a great game, recorded by Eric, published 22 January 2019.

UGH! release dates:
- C64: 1983
- Dragon 32: 1983
- TRS-80 CoCo: 1983
- ZX Spectrum: 1984

UGH! is longplay No. 311 of the Ludophiles longplays project:
- https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLFXG3BI19O5rpA9sB1_-K_x5s207hoahb
- http://www.ludophiles.com/threads/ludophiles-longplays-project.180/

UGH!  is longplay No. 160 of RecordedC64Games.org:
- https://recordedc64games.org/ugh-softek/

#ludophiles #ludophilia #c64 #retrogaming #longplay #playthrough
